  "commit_message": "Warn on prefetch={true} navigation without Partial Prefetching (dev) (#94672)\n\nUnder Cache Components, a `<Link prefetch={true}>` pointing at a route\nthat hasn't enabled Partial Prefetching quietly falls back to a legacy\nfull prefetch: it pulls down the route's dynamic data instead of just\nthe static shell, defeating the static/dynamic split. In development we\nnow surface this with a console error that explains the fallback and\npoints at how to opt in — app-wide with `partialPrefetching`, or\nper",
